	  <physDesc>
	    <supportDesc>
	      <support>An āyaka-slab, with three caitya window arches
	      with a railing in front. The upper portion has a
	      representation of two figures, and the lower part
	      has a representation of two attendants (one male
	      and one female).</support>
	    </supportDesc>
	  </physDesc>
	  <history>
